WITH filtered_dates AS (
  SELECT
    d_date_sk
  FROM date_dim
  WHERE
    d_date BETWEEN CAST('1999-02-21' AS DATE) AND (
      CAST('1999-02-21' AS DATE) + INTERVAL '60' DAY
    )
)
SELECT
  i_item_id,
  i_item_desc,
  i_current_price
FROM item, inventory, filtered_dates, catalog_sales
WHERE
  i_current_price BETWEEN 45 AND 45 + 30
  AND inv_item_sk = i_item_sk
  AND filtered_dates.d_date_sk = inv_date_sk
  AND i_manufact_id IN (856, 707, 1000, 747)
  AND inv_quantity_on_hand BETWEEN 100 AND 500
  AND cs_item_sk = i_item_sk
GROUP BY
  i_item_id,
  i_item_desc,
  i_current_price
ORDER BY
  i_item_id
LIMIT 100

FROM (

    i_item_desc,
    i_current_price
  FROM item

    i_current_price BETWEEN 45 AND 45 + 30 AND i_manufact_id IN (856, 707, 1000, 747)
) AS item, (
  SELECT
    inv_item_sk,
    inv_date_sk
  FROM inventory
  WHERE
    inv_quantity_on_hand BETWEEN 100 AND 500
) AS inventory, (
  SELECT
    d_date_sk
  FROM date_dim
  WHERE
    d_date BETWEEN CAST('1999-02-21' AS DATE) AND (
      CAST('1999-02-21' AS DATE) + INTERVAL '60' DAY
    )
) AS date_dim, catalog_sales
WHERE
  inv_item_sk = i_item_sk AND d_date_sk = inv_date_sk AND cs_item_sk = i_item_sk
GROUP BY
  i_item_id,
  i_item_desc,
  i_current_price
ORDER BY
  i_item_id
LIMIT 100

WITH filtered_items AS (
    SELECT i_item_id, i_item_desc, i_current_price, i_item_sk, i_manufact_id
    FROM item
    WHERE i_current_price BETWEEN 45 AND 75
      AND i_manufact_id IN (856,707,1000,747)
),
inventory_agg AS (
    SELECT inv_item_sk, SUM(inv_quantity_on_hand) AS total_inv_qty
    FROM inventory
    JOIN date_dim ON d_date_sk = inv_date_sk
    WHERE d_date BETWEEN CAST('1999-02-21' AS DATE) AND (CAST('1999-02-21' AS DATE) + INTERVAL 60 DAY)
    GROUP BY inv_item_sk
    HAVING SUM(inv_quantity_on_hand) BETWEEN 100 AND 500
),
catalog_sales_agg AS (
    SELECT cs_item_sk
    FROM catalog_sales
    GROUP BY cs_item_sk
)
SELECT fi.i_item_id, fi.i_item_desc, fi.i_current_price
FROM filtered_items fi
JOIN inventory_agg ia ON fi.i_item_sk = ia.inv_item_sk
JOIN catalog_sales_agg csa ON fi.i_item_sk = csa.cs_item_sk
ORDER BY fi.i_item_id
LIMIT 100

SELECT
  i_item_id,
  i_item_desc,
  i_current_price
FROM (
  SELECT
    i_item_sk,
    i_item_id,
    i_item_desc,
    i_current_price,
    i_manufact_id,
    CASE WHEN i_current_price BETWEEN 45 AND 75 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS price_condition,
    CASE WHEN i_manufact_id IN (856, 707, 1000, 747) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS manufact_condition
  FROM item
  WHERE
    i_current_price BETWEEN 45 AND 75 OR i_manufact_id IN (856, 707, 1000, 747)
) AS item_scan, inventory, date_dim, catalog_sales
WHERE
  price_condition = 1
  AND manufact_condition = 1
  AND inv_item_sk = i_item_sk
  AND d_date_sk = inv_date_sk
  AND d_date BETWEEN CAST('1999-02-21' AS DATE) AND (
    CAST('1999-02-21' AS DATE) + INTERVAL '60' DAY
  )
  AND inv_quantity_on_hand BETWEEN 100 AND 500
  AND cs_item_sk = i_item_sk
GROUP BY
  i_item_id,
  i_item_desc,
  i_current_price
ORDER BY
  i_item_id
LIMIT 100

SELECT
  i_item_id,
  i_item_desc,
  i_current_price
FROM filtered_items AS fi
JOIN filtered_inventory AS inv
  ON fi.i_item_sk = inv.inv_item_sk
JOIN filtered_dates AS dd
  ON inv.inv_date_sk = dd.d_date_sk
JOIN catalog_sales AS cs
  ON fi.i_item_sk = cs.cs_item_sk
GROUP BY
  i_item_id,
  i_item_desc,
  i_current_price
ORDER BY
  i_item_id
LIMIT 100
